column2: SELECT TOP #  p.g,p.r, s.z as redshift,p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.g BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.r BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.i BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND CLASS = &&&  AND s.z > #
